#: ../../../release/dev/list-PREDICATE.rst:2
msgid "list-PREDICATE"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/dev/list-PREDICATE.rst:4
msgid ""
"The :command:`list(TRANSFORM)` command gained a new ``PREDICATE`` selector "
"that invokes a user-defined :command:`function` to decide which elements are "
"transformed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/dev/list-PREDICATE.rst:8
msgid ""
"The :command:`list(FILTER)` command gained a new ``PREDICATE`` mode that "
"invokes a user-defined :command:`function` to decide which elements are "
"included or excluded, complementing the existing ``REGEX`` mode."
msgstr ""
